<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n12142i"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12142i">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12142i"> 142(i)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> 1<sup>st</sup> extra Roman / mission SP</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"> Un trait marque l&apos;entreprise de l&apos;ap&ocirc;tre: <mark>le premier, parmi les missionnaires</mark>, il se rend dans une terre <mark>situ&eacute;e hors des limites de l&apos;empire romain</mark>, pour y porter l&apos;&Eacute;vangile. <br><font color="green">[One distinctive characteristic of the apostle&apos;s adventure: he was the first, it seems, to bring the Gospel to a land outside of the borders of the Roman Empire.]</font> <small> Riguet, Abb&eacute; <a name="RTSP" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#RTSP"><cite title="source">Saint Patrice</cite></a> (1911) 175</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
